OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,FPeople who miss scheduled NHS
OL,7,Fappointments twice in Wales will be
OL,8,Fremoved from the waiting list, the
OL,9,FHealth Secretary has said, unless they
OL,10,Fhave a valid reason.
OL,12,FThis is one part of the Health
OL,13,FSecretary's plans to try and reduce
OL,14,Fwaiting lists and eliminate two-year
OL,15,Fwaiting times for planned treatment.
OL,17,FThe changes are being described as a
OL,18,Fnew "patient deal", with the hope they
OL,19,Fwill crack down on the 700,000
OL,20,Foutpatient appointments which are
OL,21,Fmissed or cancelled every year.
