OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,FIt says it will also implement a
OL,7,Fpolicy of only allowing people who are
OL,8,Ffit and well enough to benefit from
OL,9,Fsurgery to be added to surgical
OL,10,Ftreatment waiting list.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government has said the NHS
OL,13,Fwill support people to get in the best
OL,14,Fpossible shape for their treatment and
OL,15,Fevidence shows they are more likely to
OL,16,Frecover quickly.
OL,18,FCommenting on the plan, Mr Miles has
OL,19,Fsaid it requires effort from both the
OL,20,Fpublic and the health service.
