OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,F"The NHS will do all it can to
OL,7,Fprioritise faster access to treatment.
OL,8,FIn return, we are asking the public to
OL,9,Fdo all they can to prioritise and keep
OL,10,Ftheir appointments so, together, we
OL,11,Fmake the best possible use of scarce
OL,12,FNHS resources.
OL,14,F"We cannot continue losing as many as
OL,15,Fone in seven appointments because
OL,16,Fpeople do not turn up or cannot
OL,17,Fattend, and a further 10% which are
OL,18,Fcancelled by the NHS.
